examples.en: He was painfully sensible of his inferiority in conversation.
He always felt inferior around his brother.
Interiorly most people enjoy the inferiority of their friends.
He wrestled all his life with his feeling of inferiority.
These pearls are of inferior quality.
He had a deep-rooted feeling of inferiority.
The judges voted to overturn a ruling made by an inferior court.
They were considered a socially inferior group.
